data.description: Welcome to this charming 1 story home nestled in the desirable community of Cypress, TX. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, & 1 half bathroom. This property offers both comfort and privacy. Step inside and you will be greeted with a warm and inviting atmosphere, accentuated by natural light flowing throughout the open floor plan. The heart of the home features a well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances and ample counter space. The adjoining living room, complete with a fireplace that has never been used!  Retreat to the generously sized primary bedroom with a huge walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms all have walk-in closets  Outside, enjoy the tranquility of having no back neighbors and the security of a brick fence. Home has a covered patio, but the backyard is a blank canvas, ready for you to create your own oasis.  This home is ideally located in a peaceful neighborhood, close to schools, shopping, and dining options, making it a perfect blend of convenience & privacy
